{"tid":1681131,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"既然解放軍唔出得，咁hk 咁多軍營做乜鳩","createTime":"2019-10-29T08:29:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T03:15:33.000Z","uid":30788,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2644b90ac12f0e3c1631e8a7854077a9bbb1ff7e","tid":1681131,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T08:29:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b5dbc378108ef866418443798337af91989cd70","tid":1681131,"uid":136893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T08:30:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">記唔記得7、8月既時候，臨有行動前一日既連登，係充滿住遊行路線、離開方法、行動目的地既街坊整既攻略、仲有各種各樣既行動資訊整合，所有行動都係至小早半個月搞，有D 活動更加係會根據其重要性去調配，例如我記得葵青區遊行係推遲左成個月的。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n反思行動及行動數量<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">（極緊急！！！）等我教大家點再引發群眾熱情<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680895\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680895</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"fcccc98a28d95c9638c3afb8cb0dc8c630780d22","tid":1681131,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T08:31:31.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，推post &amp; 借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港民調，追蹤長期民意，做份國際文宣，話比全世界聽， 5毛網軍不代表香港人(眾籌到而家先30%, 仲要大家支持) <br />\n<br />\n連登post: 鍾庭耀教授都企左出來....你仲做冷氣軍師??<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n眾籌link: <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg9qUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=54cc72da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a>"},{"pid":"b9debde01ce5458e6b7f253e7eac32a29d2bc7f9","tid":1681131,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T08:32:09.000Z","msg":"強積金都係動用唔到 我都